hh3cVMMan.name: hh3cVMMan
hh3cVMMan.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cVMMan.description: VM is one of surveillance features, implementing user authentication, configuration management, network management and control signalling forwarding. This MIB contains objects to manage the VM feature.

hh3cVMCapabilitySet.name: hh3cVMCapabilitySet
hh3cVMCapabilitySet.description: Components included in the VM feature represented by bit fields. VM feature includes three componets: CMS(Central Management Server), CSS(Control Signalling Server) and DM(Data Managment). A bit set to 1 indicates the corresponding component of this bit is included otherwise indicates the corresponding component of this bit is not included. VM can include one or more components at one time.
